The paper discusses the use of electromagnetic interference (EMI) for load disaggregation, which falls under the category of smart grid technology and energy management systems. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for identifying appliances, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses simulations and measurements, which could fall under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper involves signal processing techniques, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory).
